inimize operational and security concerns across and beyond the enterprise; and network management and defense services for operating, maintaining, and defending complex enterprise networks. It serves the United States federal government, large commercial businesses, state and local governments, and international customers. Telos Corporation was founded in 1968 and is headquartered in Ashburn, Virginia.", "fullTimeEmployees": 509, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. John B. Wood", "age": 61, "title": "President, Chairman & CEO", "yearBorn": 1964, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 648200, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Gary Mark Bendza", "age": 48, "title": "Executive VP & CFO", "yearBorn": 1977, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 419384, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. E. Hutchinson Robbins Jr.", "age": 57, "title": "Executive VP & General Counsel", "yearBorn": 1968, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 434424, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Mark D. Griffin", "age": 65, "title": "Executive Vice President of Security Solutions", "yearBorn": 1960, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 425639, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Malcolm G. Cooke", "age": 49, "title": "VP & Chief Information Technology Officer", "yearBorn": 1976, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 298293, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Donald Joseph Terreri CPA", "age": 42, "title": "Controller & Chief Accounting Officer", "yearBorn": 1983, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Christina  Mouzavires", "title": "Investor Relations Officer", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Allison  Phillipp", "title": "Director of Communications", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name